INSERT INTO forum_article VALUES(1,'【参赛作品】智慧大棚','随着科技时代的发展，智能化系统的应用渗入各个领域，智慧大棚利用智能化系统，模拟出植物生长环境，基于OneNET平台控制大棚内对温度、湿度、火焰、可燃气体、水位，光照等进行智能监测，大棚主要由两大部分构成：一部分为智慧大棚；另一部分为露天大棚。这两部分进行鲜明对比，凸显出智慧大棚的优点。有了理论基础后，我们利用沙盘来呈现，从而更直观的了解','article_img/2021/05/16/微信截图_20210516011102.png','<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="999" style="width: 768px;"><tbody style="overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><tr style="overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;" class="firstRow"><td class="t_f" data-id="adf6" id="postmessage_41830" style="overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-all;"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span style="overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 15pt;">【个人</span></span><span style="overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 15pt;">/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span style="overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 15pt;">团队介绍】：一群物联网发烧友</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体;overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span style="overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 15pt;">【正文】</span></span><span style="overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 15pt;"></span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体;overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span style="overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 15pt;">简介：</span></span><span style="overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 15pt;"></span></p><p>随着科技时代的发展，智能化系统的应用渗入各个领域，智慧大棚利用智能化系统，模拟出植物生长环境，基于OneNET平台控制大棚内对温度、湿度、火焰、可燃气体、水位，光照等进行智能监测，大棚主要由两大部分构成：一部分为智慧大棚；另一部分为露天大棚。这两部分进行鲜明对比，凸显出智慧大棚的优点。有了理论基础后，我们利用沙盘来呈现，从而更直观的了解智能化系统。智慧大棚不仅避免造成人为因素而造成的生产损失。还能提高了农作物的产量和质量并很大一部分降低劳动成本。</p><br style="overflow-wrap: break-word;"/><p><span style="font-family:宋体;overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span style="overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 15pt;">功能：</span></span><span style="overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 15pt;"></span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体;overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span style="overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 15pt;">1.</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span style="overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 15pt;">使用者可用网页或者手机 APP 对大棚的当前状态进行查看,同时也可以进行相应的操作。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体;overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span style="overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 15pt;">2.</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span style="overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 15pt;">大棚内设有温度、土壤湿度、火焰、可燃气体、水位，光照传感器，通过温度传感器对大棚内温度进行可控监控，如果温度大于设定阈值，自动打开大棚散热系统进行散热；土壤传感器检测土壤的相对湿度，湿度过低灌溉系统对大棚植物进行自动灌溉；火焰以及可燃气体检测传感器，对明火和可燃气体进行实时监控，若有意外火灾触发报警系统通风系统；通水位传感器对蓄水箱内水位进行监控，水位低于设定阈值时触发报警；植物生长离不开光照，通过RGB灯我们可以给植物提供他们需要的光。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体;overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span style="overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 15pt;">3.</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span style="overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 15pt;">通过网页或手机 app 我们可以控制散热系统散热；灌溉系统进行灌溉；控制RGB灯，提供不同颜色的光。</span></span><span style="overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 15pt;"></span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体;overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span style="overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 15pt;">应用链接：</span></span></p><p><span style="overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 15pt;"></span><a href="http://open.iot.10086.cn/appview/p/beed924608398c90a052c2c0a75346ed" target="_blank" class="gj_safe_a" style="overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);">https://open.iot.10086.cn/appview/p/beed924608398c90a052c2c0a75346ed</a></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体;overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span style="overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 15pt;">视频链接：</span></span></p><p><span style="overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 15pt;"><a href="http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMjgwNzg4NjkxMg==.html?from=s1.8-1-1.2&spm=a2h0k.8191407.0.0" target="_blank" class="gj_safe_a" style="overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px;">http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMjgwNzg4NjkxMg==.html?from=s1.8-1-1.2&amp;spm=a2h0k.8191407.0.0</a></span></p><br style="overflow-wrap: break-word;"/><p><span style="font-family:宋体;overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span style="font-size:18px;overflow-wrap: break-word;">源码下载链接：</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体;overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span style="font-size:18px;overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span style="color:#555555;overflow-wrap: break-word;">链接:&nbsp;<a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1kV3InlH" target="_blank" class="gj_safe_a" style="overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px;">https://pan.baidu.com/s/1kV3InlH</a>&nbsp; &nbsp; 密码: gghv</span></span></span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体;overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span style="font-size:18px;overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span style="color:#ff8c00;overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span style="overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;">复制在新页面打开！！！！</span></span></span></span></p><br style="overflow-wrap: break-word;"/><p><ignore_js_op style="overflow-wrap: break-word;"><img id="aimg_3395" aid="3395" src="http://upfiles.heclouds.com/forum-app/2017/06/06/45a773b838714c2cc02068833c0aba75.jpg" zoomfile="http://upfiles.heclouds.com/forum-app/2017/06/06/45a773b838714c2cc02068833c0aba75.jpg" file="http://upfiles.heclouds.com/forum-app/2017/06/06/45a773b838714c2cc02068833c0aba75.jpg" inpost="1" style="overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 999px;"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op><ignore_js_op style="overflow-wrap: break-word;"><img id="aimg_3396" aid="3396" src="http://upfiles.heclouds.com/forum-app/2017/06/06/e669514e4336aa84f6f484f6e7b2d072.jpg" zoomfile="http://upfiles.heclouds.com/forum-app/2017/06/06/e669514e4336aa84f6f484f6e7b2d072.jpg" file="http://upfiles.heclouds.com/forum-app/2017/06/06/e669514e4336aa84f6f484f6e7b2d072.jpg" inpost="1" initialized="true" style="overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 999px;"/></ignore_js_op></p><br style="overflow-wrap: break-word;"/><br style="overflow-wrap: break-word;"/></td></tr></tbody></table><p><br/></p><p class="mbn" style="overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><br/><br/></p><p><img id="aimg_3398" aid="3398" src="http://upfiles.heclouds.com/forum-app/2017/06/06/d694babaab70e347007bdccfd2a81e4f.png" zoomfile="http://upfiles.heclouds.com/forum-app/2017/06/06/d694babaab70e347007bdccfd2a81e4f.png" file="http://upfiles.heclouds.com/forum-app/2017/06/06/d694babaab70e347007bdccfd2a81e4f.png" alt="4)W_B1`0$MZ{)ITJN18(%H0.png" title="4)W_B1`0$MZ{)ITJN18(%H0.png" w="556" style="overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 999px;"/></p><p><ignore_js_op style="overflow-wrap: break-word;"></ignore_js_op></p><ul class="tattl attm list-paddingleft-2" style="overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 10px 10px 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; float: none; overflow: visible; width: 999px; height: auto;"><li><p class="mbn" style="overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><br/></p><p><img id="aimg_3399" aid="3399" src="http://upfiles.heclouds.com/forum-app/2017/06/06/e8cc391e075793a130f885dc2c1c1bb8.jpg" zoomfile="http://upfiles.heclouds.com/forum-app/2017/06/06/e8cc391e075793a130f885dc2c1c1bb8.jpg" file="http://upfiles.heclouds.com/forum-app/2017/06/06/e8cc391e075793a130f885dc2c1c1bb8.jpg" alt="IMG20170606153740.jpg" title="IMG20170606153740.jpg" w="4160" style="overflow-wrap: break