INSERT INTO forum_article VALUES(2,'物联网与数据可视化的结合：农业领域中的智慧大棚系统','伴随着科技飞速发展，面朝黄土背朝天的农耕时代已经变成历史，智慧农业这一理念走入寻常百姓家。所谓的智慧农业就是充分利用现代信息技术发展的成果，结合传统农业，将物联网技术切合实际的运用到传统农业中。在智慧农业的大力发展的背景下，智慧大棚的诞生是顺其自然的，是智慧农业不可或缺的一部分。大棚应用物联网技术，可达到改善产品品质、调节生长周期、提高经济效益的目的，尤其是可实现温室大棚管理的高效和精准，且在规模','article_img/2021/05/16/4.jpg','<h3 id="%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80" name="%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80" style="margin: 16px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">前言</strong></h3><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">伴随着科技飞速发展，面朝黄土背朝天的农耕时代已经变成历史，<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">智慧农业</strong>这一理念走入寻常百姓家。所谓的<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">智慧农业</strong>就是充分利用现代信息技术发展的成果，结合传统农业，将物联网技术切合实际的运用到传统农业中。在<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">智慧农业</strong>的大力发展的背景下，<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">智慧大棚</strong>的诞生是顺其自然的，是<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">智慧农业</strong>不可或缺的一部分。大棚应用物联网技术，可达到改善产品品质、调节生长周期、提高经济效益的目的，尤其是可实现温室大棚管理的高效和精准，且在规模化的大棚设施而言，运用“智慧大棚”可以在最短的时间内完成调控，极大的降低了劳动成本。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　介于 <strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">2D</strong> 组态和 <strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">3D</strong> 组态上，<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">Hightopo</strong>（以下简称 <strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">HT</strong>）的 <strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">HT for Web</strong> 产品上的有着丰富的组态化可供选择，本文将介绍如何运用 <strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">HT</strong> 丰富的 <strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">2/3D</strong> 组态搭建出一个<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">智慧大棚</strong>。</p><h3 id="%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B%E5%8F%8A%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%E9%A2%84%E8%A7%88" name="%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B%E5%8F%8A%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%E9%A2%84%E8%A7%88" style="margin: 16px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">界面简介及效果预览</strong></h3><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　在<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">智慧大棚</strong>中，模拟呈现了温室大棚的环境。可以在<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">智慧大棚</strong>中控制遮阳网、灌溉、补光灯、风扇、气流显示的开启和关闭，并且模拟农作物的生长过程。在接入物联网系统的温度传感器、湿度传感器、光感器、CO2传感器后，可以做到便捷快速的管理农业大棚。</p><p></p><figure style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; margin: 16px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;"><img src="https://ask.qcloudimg.com/http-save/7454122/eqe9dluh9q.gif" class="" style="border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; display: block; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; box-shadow: rgba(3, 27, 78, 0.12) 0px 4px 8px; border-radius: 3px; cursor: zoom-in;"/></span></p></figure><p></p><h3 id="%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7%E5%A4%A7%E6%A3%9A%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%B7%E5%80%BC" name="%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7%E5%A4%A7%E6%A3%9A%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%B7%E5%80%BC" style="margin: 16px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">智慧大棚实现价值</strong></h3><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　通过物联网和现代农业结合，远程控制的实现工作人员在任何有网络的地方就能够对大棚的环境进行监控，并且根据监控到的大棚状态，控制大棚的生长环境。可以采用无线网络的实现农作物的精准种植，以达到节本增效。智能大棚在运用得当的情况下，还可以达到以下效果：</p><h4 id="1%E3%80%81%E5%86%9C%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E8%BF%BD%E6%BA%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F" name="1%E3%80%81%E5%86%9C%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E8%BF%BD%E6%BA%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">1、农产品质量安全追溯系统</strong></h4><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　采集各地块播种、施肥、灌溉、除草等农事操作记录，生产环境数据，全生长周期高清图片，实现生产环节可追溯。以农业生产者的生产档案信息为基础，实现对基础信息、生产过程信息等的实时记、生产操作预警，生产档案查询和上传功能。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　食品安全追溯系统在食品供应链中提供完全透明的管理能力，保障食品安全全程可视化控制、监控与追溯，可以全程监控食品生产、加工过程的添加剂以及有害物质、流通环节中的安全隐患。对有可能出现的食品安全隐患进行有效评估和科学预警提供依据。数据能够通过网络实现实时、准确报送，便于快速高效做更深层次的分析研究。消费者可查询所购买食品的完整追踪信息。</p><h4 id="2%E3%80%81%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E5%A4%A7%E6%A3%9A%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6" name="2%E3%80%81%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E5%A4%A7%E6%A3%9A%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">2、智能大棚控制</strong></h4><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　在手机上即可远程手动控制多个大棚的设施设备，包括风机、外遮阳、内遮阳、喷滴灌、侧窗、水帘、阀门、加温灯等。根据时间、气象数据、土壤数据等，系统可按照设定规则，自动进行灌溉、通风、开关天窗等操作。</p><h4 id="3%E3%80%81%E6%B0%B4%E8%82%A5%E4%B8%80%E4%BD%93%E5%8C%96%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E7%81%8C%E6%BA%89%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F" name="3%E3%80%81%E6%B0%B4%E8%82%A5%E4%B8%80%E4%BD%93%E5%8C%96%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E7%81%8C%E6%BA%89%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">3、水肥一体化自动灌溉系统</strong></h4><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　通过可控管道系统供水、供肥，是水肥相融后通过管道、喷枪或喷头进行喷灌，均匀、定时、定量的喷洒再作物发育生长区域，是主要发育生长区域徒然始终保持疏松和适宜的含水量，同时根据不同的作物的需肥特点，徒然环境和养分含量状况，把水分、养分定时定量，按比例直接提供给作物。</p><h4 id="4%E3%80%81-%E7%97%85%E8%99%AB%E5%AE%B3%E8%AF%8A%E6%96%AD%E9%98%B2%E6%B2%BB%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F" name="4%E3%80%81-%E7%97%85%E8%99%AB%E5%AE%B3%E8%AF%8A%E6%96%AD%E9%98%B2%E6%B2%BB%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">4、 病虫害诊断防治系统</strong></h4><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　用户发现作物出现异常时，可通过手机拍摄作物叶片或者果实上传到云平台，即可在毫秒内识别作物是否患有病虫害，患有什么病虫害，并获得防治措施，让你快速确诊，准确用药，避免延误病情，造成损失。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　（1）系统可实现害虫类别自动分类及计数，并自动进行无公害诱捕杀虫，减少农药的使用；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　（2）通过高清摄像机采集虫情图像，可远程查看田间虫情，并制定防治措施。</p><h4 id="5%E3%80%81%E6%B0%94%E8%B1%A1%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9B%91%E6%B5%8B" name="5%E3%80%81%E6%B0%94%E8%B1%A1%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9B%91%E6%B5%8B" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">5、气象环境监测</strong></h4><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　实时监测空气温湿度、光照、降雨量、风速、风向、大气压力、气体浓度等数据，并通过设定相关报警阈值，实现即时报警，精准控制种植环境指标。根据卫星数据，系统可预报未来72小时气象，24小时极端天气、降水概率、大风等异常气象预警，提醒用户及时做好防灾防险准备。</p><h4 id="6%E3%80%81%E5%9C%9F%E5%A3%A4%E5%A2%92%E6%83%85%E7%9B%91%E6%B5%8B" name="6%E3%80%81%E5%9C%9F%E5%A3%A4%E5%A2%92%E6%83%85%E7%9B%91%E6%B5%8B" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">6、土壤墒情监测</strong></h4><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　土壤墒情精准监测，异常情况快速预警；实时监测土壤水张力、土壤温湿度、水位、溶氧量、pH值等。通过设定报警阈值，当土壤数据异常时，如湿度过高，系统自动发出预警消息提醒工作人员。</p><h4 id="7%E3%80%81%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F" name="7%E3%80%81%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">7、视频监控系统</strong></h4><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　无人机精准测绘，全程自主飞行，任何地形随时作业；定位地块位置、识别地块分界、测算地块面积；在电子地图上圈画地块直观展示；通过720度高清摄像，突发情况可自动转向紧急录像，进行作物长势监测；高清摄像头可720度旋转、拉近、拉远，查看园区实时生产情况；发生预警时，摄像头可自动转向到预警点紧急录像，不放过任何异常；可对视频进行截图，无需另外安装相机进行拍摄。</p><h4 id="8%E3%80%81%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F" name="8%E3%80%81%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">8、设施远程控制系统</strong></h4><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　通过远程控制系统，用户可以远程查看设施环境数据和设备运行情况，还可以分析数据，方便灵活管理。可实现根据种植预设条件，自动控制增温、降温、通风、灌溉、施肥等设备的运行，满足严苛的农作物种植环境条件要求，减少不必要的损失，同时可以节省用电，降低生产成本。</p><h3 id="%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90" name="%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90" style="margin: 16px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">系统分析</strong></h3><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">智慧大棚</strong>是将智能化控制应用到大棚种植中，获取到大棚内部的环境（如：空气温度、空气湿 度、二化碳、光照、土壤温度、土壤湿度、肥力-氮磷钾等）和气象环境（如：室外空气温度、空气湿度、风速、风向、光照等），对比设置环境阈值（各环境参数的正常范围值）和设置实际值，当实际值超出环境阈值时，要采取相应的措施（预警、自动/手动控制设备调节环境）。</p><h4 id="1%E3%80%81%E5%A4%A7%E6%A3%9A%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%EF%BC%9A" name="1%E3%80%81%E5%A4%A7%E6%A3%9A%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%EF%BC%9A" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">1、大棚管理：</strong></h4><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">通过在页面上的操作可以手动开关遮阳网、灌溉、补光灯、风扇、气流显示。<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">智慧大棚</strong>可以根据时间、气象数据、土壤数据等，系统会按照设定规则自动开启/关闭设备。</p><p></p><figure style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; margin: 16px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;"><img src="https://ask.qcloudimg.com/http-save/7454122/1fzoko2tbr.png?imageView2/2/w/1620" class="" style="border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; display: block; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; box-shadow: rgba(3, 27, 78, 0.12) 0px 4px 8px; border-radius: 3px; cursor: zoom-in;"/></span></p></figure><p></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">大棚管理主要分为以下几个部分：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（1）遮阳网：遮阳网可以控制光照的强弱、时长等，可以根据不同农作物的不同生长阶段对关照强度和时长的需求进行调整。有效的保障了农作物的健康生长，并且可以延长农作物的生长期，达到增产的效果；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（2）灌溉：在读取到大棚内的温度和湿度后，根据不同的农作物多土壤湿度的不同要求设置最适宜湿度，完成自动灌溉，减少人工劳动和对水资源的浪费；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（3）补光灯： 温室大棚光照与作物的生长有密切的关系。最大限度的捕捉光能，充分发挥植物光合作用的潜力，将直接关系到农业生产的效益。室补光灯，也叫植物补光灯，是依照植物生长的自然规律，根据植物利用太阳光进行光合作用的原理,使用灯光代替太阳光来提供给温室植物生长发育所需光源；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（4）风扇：风扇是大棚控温、自动通风换气的不可缺少的一部分，风扇可以智能呢个控制风口，自动调节大棚温度。最高效的利用大棚内的温度资源，提高农作物的品质和产量。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（5）显示气流：气流显示可以帮助管理人员有效的看到气流的状态，便于管理大棚。</p><h4 id="2%E3%80%81%E5%86%9C%E4%BD%9C%E7%89%A9%E6%A8%A1%E6%8B%9F%E7%94%9F%E9%95%BF%EF%BC%9A" name="2%E3%80%81%E5%86%9C%E4%BD%9C%E7%89%A9%E6%A8%A1%E6%8B%9F%E7%94%9F%E9%95%BF%EF%BC%9A" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">2、农作物模拟生长：</strong></h4><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">在系统中每隔90s循环模拟一次植物的生长过程，农作物在生长过程中的种子、发芽、幼苗、成苗小、成苗中、成苗大、开花、成熟、枯萎的状态一一展现，还可以手动控制展示农作物的生长状态。</p><p></p><figure style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; margin: 16px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;"><img src="https://ask.qcloudimg.com/http-save/7454122/kwrkj0w2e9.gif" class="" style="border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; display: block; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; box-shadow: rgba(3, 27, 78, 0.12) 0px 4px 8px; border-radius: 3px; cursor: zoom-in;"/></span></p></figure><p></p><h3 id="%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93" name="%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93" style="margin: 16px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">总结</strong></h3><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">如今<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">智慧农业</strong>已经到达了一个相对成熟的阶段，各种形式的智能温室大棚不断出现在实际生产种植中，<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">智慧大棚</strong>是顺应时代发展的产物，将网络信息技术应用到温室大棚的控制系统中必然发展成一种潮流。中国人民的生活水平不断提升，对蔬菜与水果的需求也只会越来越高，果蔬的成色好、味道好是产品价格的决定特点，因此，智能大棚的发展只会愈加的迅速，采用传统人工管理的大棚会被逐渐淘汰。而 <strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">HT</strong> 开发的<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit;">智慧大棚</strong>有助于使用者在电脑上更直观的看到大棚内的情况，真正做到足不出户就可以管理大棚。</p><p><br/></p>',18,'2021-05-15 17:36:57.409801','2021-05-16 12:16:26.683003',1,1,2);
INSERT INTO forum_article VALUES(3,'种菜用上高科技 “智慧大棚”助农增收','中新网山西新闻4月17日电 (吴琼 冯静宁) “通过传感器，我们能直观地看到水果、蔬菜的情况，让农作物‘渴了有水喝，饿了有肥料’。”16日，山西省晋中市榆次区北田镇的种植户张秀琴第一次走进现代化玻璃温室，咨询学习现代农业技术。','article_img/2021/05/16/1.jpg','<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;">中新网山西新闻4月17日电 (吴琼 冯静宁) “通过传感器，我们能直观地看到水果、蔬菜的情况，让农作物‘渴了有水喝，饿了有肥料’。”16日，山西省晋中市榆次区北田镇的种植户张秀琴第一次走进现代化玻璃温室，咨询学习现代农业技术。</p><p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;">　　人工智能、物联网、大数据技术赋能农业种植，“猪联网”升级实现远程化监管……近年来，晋中国家农高区(山西农谷)持续强化“高新”发展内核，发挥“领跑”作用，在山西农业现代化和乡村振兴中的“头雁”效应日益显现。</p><p><img src="http://www.sx.chinanews.com/2021/0417/U989P8DT20210417152431.png" style="width: 550.797px; height: 309.828px; margin: 0px; border: 0px;"/><span class="img_descr" style="display: block;">温枭 摄</span></p><p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;">　　近日，在山西农谷东辉世佳农业科技有限公司内，集人工智能、5G、物联网、大数据赋能的智慧大棚，吸引一批批农户前来观摩学习。</p><p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;">　　张强军是这里的技术员，主要负责管理园区内3个荷兰模式设施大棚以及培训棚长等工作。从山西农业大学毕业后，他已扎根农业10余年。“这些天，我每天向来访农户介绍现代农业种植技术和农业生产管理理念，并且了解、记下大家的需求，解答农户问题。”张强军说。</p><p><img src="http://www.sx.chinanews.com/2021/0417/U989P8DT20210417152447.png" style="width: 550.797px; height: 309.828px; margin: 0px; border: 0px;"/><span class="img_descr" style="display: block;">温枭 摄</span></p><p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;">　　山西东辉世佳农业科技有限公司是晋中国家农高区孵化的一家现代农业示范企业，该公司围绕新技术、新品种、新装备、新设施，展开试验示范并深度拓宽和农户的合作模式，帮助农户增收。</p><p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;">　　借助合作模式，太谷区范村镇象谷村桑黎娜一家的生活实现了转变。从过去自己依靠经验种苗施肥，四处奔波销售蔬菜，到现在公司提供技术指导并负责收购，桑黎娜说，“科学种田省心省力，我们计划掌握更多种植技术，投资几个大棚。”</p><p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;">　　目前，该公司与周边15户种植户签订合作协议，带动150余人就业，每户年平均收入可提高2万至3万元。</p><p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;">　　“现在，流转土地的2700多元加上公司发的工资，一年能挣4万多元。”56岁的农户薛拴民告诉记者，2019年，他将自己的3亩地流转给上述公司，不仅收入翻番，还学到先进技术，为今后自己创业积累“资本”。(完)</p><p><br/></p>',101,'2021-05-15 17:42:39.139911','2021-05-16 06:47:30.987932',2,1,3);
INSERT INTO forum_article VALUES(4,'智能大棚工程建设设计方案','目前来说，智能大棚也不是什么特别神奇的存在，它已经成为现代设施农业发展主要的一项技术指标，经常会接到一些客户的电话咨询，我想做智能大棚，那么智能大棚都能实现什么功能，那么今天就和大家简单聊下经常用的一些系统，智能大棚就是在日光温室、薄膜温室、阳光板温室、玻璃温室等传统温室的基础上，利用物联网的技术，通过无线传感器网络一个测量控制区，采用不同的传感器节点和具有简单执行机构的节点，文章由广源温室工程张','article_img/2021/05/16/v2-0b5b52bb9348473acfea239e506f6b95_1440w.jpg','<figure data-size="normal" style="margin: 1.4em 0px; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-91d3497dea82926393d79710062cac9d_720w.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="1500" data-rawheight="898" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1500" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-91d3497dea82926393d79710062cac9d_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-91d3497dea82926393d79710062cac9d_b.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok" style="display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; cursor: zoom-in; background-color: transparent; animation: 0.5s ease-in 0s 1 normal none running fxRichTextFadeIn;"/></figure><p style="margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">玻璃温室</p><p style="margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">目前来说，智能大棚也不是什么特别神奇的存在，它已经成为现代设施农业发展主要的一项技术指标，经常会接到一些客户的电话咨询，我想做智能大棚，那么智能大棚都能实现什么功能，那么今天就和大家简单聊下经常用的一些系统，智能大棚就是在日光温室、薄膜温室、阳光板温室、玻璃温室等传统温室的基础上，利用物联网的技术，通过无线传感器网络一个测量控制区，采用不同的传感器节点和具有简单执行机构的节点，文章由广源温室工程张经理原创发布，如有转载请保留版权信息，谢谢合作。如风机、低压电机、阀门等工作电流偏低的执行机构，构成无线网络，来测量基质湿度、成分、pH值、温度以及空气湿度、气压、光照强度、二氧化碳浓度等，再通过模型分析，自动调控温室环境、控制灌溉和施肥作业，从而获得植物生长的最佳条件。</p><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph" style="margin-top: -0.8em; margin-bottom: -0.8em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></p><p><figure data-size="normal" style="margin: 1.4em 0px; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-e1364e0ef664775d140143229820cf97_720w.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="1119" data-rawheight="716" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1119" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e1364e0ef664775d140143229820cf97_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e1364e0ef664775d140143229820cf97_b.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok" style="display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; cursor: zoom-in; background-color: transparent; animation: 0.5s ease-in 0s 1 normal none running fxRichTextFadeIn;"/></figure></p><p style="margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">智能气象站</p><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph" style="margin-top: -0.8em; margin-bottom: -0.8em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></p><p><figure data-size="normal" style="margin: 1.4em 0px; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-5019f27a3c94a91fe17376f042ccebe2_720w.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="768" data-rawheight="1178" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="768" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-5019f27a3c94a91fe17376f042ccebe2_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-5019f27a3c94a91fe17376f042ccebe2_b.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok" style="display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; cursor: zoom-in; background-color: transparent; animation: 0.5s ease-in 0s 1 normal none running fxRichTextFadeIn;"/></figure></p><p style="margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">智能气象站</p><p style="margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">智能气象站</p><p style="margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">智能气象站是一体化结构设计，外形美观，安装方便简捷，可靠运行于各种环境，使用方便，数据测量精度高，可采集温度、湿度、风向、风速、太阳辐射、雨量、气压、光照度、土壤温度、土壤湿度等多项信息并做公告和趋势分析，该系统分有线站和无线站两种形式，配合软件更可以实现网络远程数据传输和网络实时气象状况监测。</p><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph" style="margin-top: -0.8em; margin-bottom: -0.8em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></p><p><figure data-size="normal" style="margin: 1.4em 0px; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-50c6007792941ceb1a470afa9c5ac1ae_720w.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="1015" data-rawheight="792" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1015" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-50c6007792941ceb1a470afa9c5ac1ae_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-50c6007792941ceb1a470afa9c5ac1ae_b.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok" style="display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; cursor: zoom-in; background-color: transparent; animation: 0.5s ease-in 0s 1 normal none running fxRichTextFadeIn;"/></figure></p><p style="margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">虫情测报</p><p style="margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">虫情测报</p><p style="margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">工作原理虫情测报灯通过灯光吸引害虫，当害虫靠近灯光后会撞击到灯管周围的玻璃，害虫撞击晕眩后就会落入测报灯下面的接虫箱中，害虫落入后，在里面会被烘干烘干后，害虫进入接虫盘上，在盘子上的害虫，通过设备内部的相机拍照，拍摄的照片可以通过无线的传输方式，传送至后台电脑端。</p><p style="margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">采集端</p><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph" style="margin-top: -0.8em; margin-bottom: -0.8em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></p><p><figure data-size="normal" style="margin: 1.4em 0px; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><p><img class="ztext-gif GifPlayer-gif2mp4Image" role="presentation" src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-89ecfea683e385b8f0096be61ab977c8_b.jpg" data-thumbnail="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-89ecfea683e385b8f0096be61ab977c8_b.jpg" data-size="normal" style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: top;"/><svg width="60" height="60" viewbox="0 0 60 60" class="GifPlayer-icon"><g fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><ellipse fill="#000" opacity="0.45" cx="30" cy="30" rx="30" ry="30"></ellipse><ellipse stroke="#FFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-dasharray="4,1,4" cx="30" cy="30" rx="26" ry="26"></ellipse><svg x="16" y="18.5" class="GifPlayer-icon"><path d="M12.842 12.981V11.4H7.64v1.653h3.27v.272c-.018 1.881-1.442 3.147-3.516 3.147-2.382 0-3.876-1.846-3.876-4.834 0-2.936 1.485-4.79 3.832-4.79 1.732 0 2.936.835 3.428 2.364h1.977c-.43-2.566-2.522-4.201-5.405-4.201-3.55 0-5.845 2.601-5.845 6.644 0 4.096 2.268 6.654 5.863 6.654 3.322 0 5.475-2.083 5.475-5.327zM17.518 18V5.317H15.55V18h1.97zm5.142 0v-5.256h5.449v-1.74h-5.45V7.11h5.95V5.317h-7.918V18h1.969z" fill="#fff"></path></svg></g></svg></p></figure></p><p style="margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">传感器</p><p style="margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">要实现对大棚内环境的实时监测，给出相对较全面的环境情况，需要布置各种各样的传感器，例如：温度传感器(空气、土壤)、光照传感器、二氧化碳浓度传感器通过部署在农业生产现场部署各种采集器、传感器等物联网设备，实时采集生产现场环境数据、设备状态数据等，并及时上传至云端，用户通过手机或者电脑登陆智慧农业物联网监控系统，即可查看园气象数据、土壤墒情、设备状态等。如遇到异常情况，系统会自动发出报警，提醒工作人员及时处理异常，或由系统自动处理解除异常。</p><p style="margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">气象数据：空气温度、空气湿度、光照时长、光照强度、风速、风向、二氧化碳浓度</p><p style="margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">土壤墒情：土壤温度、土壤含水量、土壤酸碱度</p><p style="margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">设备状态：水泵压力、水肥流量、设备运行记录</p><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph" style="margin-top: -0.8em; margin-bottom: -0.8em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></p><p><figure data-size="normal" style="margin: 1.4em 0px; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-e7c5c74049e5bab3be1e31a7448083ac_720w.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="1024" data-rawheight="852" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1024" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e7c5c74049e5bab3be1e31a7448083ac_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e7c5c74049e5bab3be1e31a7448083ac_b.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok" style="display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; cursor: zoom-in; background-color: transparent; animation: 0.5s ease-in 0s 1 normal none running fxRichTextFadeIn;"/></figure></p><p style="margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">智能大棚系统</p><p style="margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">控制端</p><p style="margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">想要真正实现温室大棚智能化，不仅需要数据的采集上传，还需要能应对情况变化的智能控制。通过智能大棚平台的网关控制器，可以外接多路设备，以实现时控制大棚内环境的效果。为了便于日后方便管理运行，标准的智能大棚玻璃大棚在建设时配备了湿帘水泵，排风机，开窗电机，遮阳电机等相关电机，智慧农业控制系统集成这些电机，通过手机APP实现远程监测大棚内数据和自动操控这些电机的运转，创造大棚内植物的良好的生长环境。系统可以制定作物生长计划与策略，可实现传感器与控制器联动自动控制，无须人工参与，即系统可以根据采集到的实时环境数据，自动远程启停控制生产现场的设备，自动实现通风、灌溉、卷帘等自动操作。用户也可通过手机在系统中进行手动远程控制。现场控制器内置智能芯片程序通过授权可自动控制生产设备，确保断网无信号等特殊情况下，仍然能保持正常工作。</p><p style="margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">监控系统</p><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph" style="margin-top: -0.8em; margin-bottom: -0.8em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></p><p><figure data-size="normal" style="margin: 1.4em 0px; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><p><img class="ztext-gif GifPlayer-gif2mp4Image" role="presentation" src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e41de9d1f003107d8f53e6cd121918bf_b.jpg" data-thumbnail="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e41de9d1f003107d8f53e6cd121918bf_b.jpg" data-size="normal" style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: top;"/><svg width="60" height="60" viewbox="0 0 60 60" class="GifPlayer-icon"><g fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><ellipse fill="#000" opacity="0.45" cx="30" cy="30" rx="30" ry="30"></ellipse><ellipse stroke="#FFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-dasharray="4,1,4" cx="30" cy="30" rx="26" ry="26"></ellipse><svg x="16" y="18.5" class="GifPlayer-icon"><path d="M12.842 12.981V11.4H7.64v1.653h3.27v.272c-.018 1.881-1.442 3.147-3.516 3.147-2.382 0-3.876-1.846-3.876-4.834 0-2.936 1.485-4.79 3.832-4.79 1.732 0 2.936.835 3.428 2.364h1.977c-.43-2.566-2.522-4.201-5.405-4.201-3.55 0-5.845 2.601-5.845 6.644 0 4.096 2.268 6.654 5.863 6.654 3.322 0 5.475-2.083 5.475-5.327zM17.518 18V5.317H15.55V18h1.97zm5.142 0v-5.256h5.449v-1.74h-5.45V7.11h5.95V5.317h-7.918V18h1.969z" fill="#fff"></path></svg></g></svg></p></figure></p><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph" style="margin-top: -0.8em; margin-bottom: -0.8em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">实时视频24小时监控，随时回放系统可扩展集成监控摄像头，生产现场安装监控设备后，用户可通过手机或者电脑就可以对作物情况、农产生产情况进行远程异地查看。同时支持视频录像，视频回放。</p><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph" style="margin-top: -0.8em; margin-bottom: -0.8em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></p><p><figure data-size="normal" style="margin: 1.4em 0px; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-2142008676e9f468b54994229a517659_720w.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="1080" data-rawheight="608" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1080" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2142008676e9f468b54994229a517659_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2142008676e9f468b54994229a517659_b.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok" style="display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; cursor: zoom-in; background-color: transparent; animation: 0.5s ease-in 0s 1 normal none running fxRichTextFadeIn;"/></figure></p><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph" style="margin-top: -0.8em; margin-bottom: -0.8em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">我国从古至今作为农业大国，农耕技术一直保持着高速发展，特别是在近几十年以来，全国的温室大棚数量不断增长。随着科技的发展，在未来，温室大棚物联网化、智能化为智慧大棚将是农业界不可避免的发展趋势。但是也要全面考虑到温室的实际使用功能，是不是真正有这个需求，合理选择恰当的配套设备，实现良好的价格性能比。广源温室张经理，温室设计、温室预算、温室工程问题可以私信或者下方留言，也可以关注“广源温室工程” 通过公众号了解更多干货。</p><p><br/></p>',153,'2021-05-15 18:09:26.593558','2021-05-16 04:53:29.422922',1,1,2);
